Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:01.410 --> 00:00:02.660
MALE SPEAKER: Hello, everyone.

00:00:02.660 --> 00:00:03.920
Thank you all for coming.

00:00:03.920 --> 00:00:08.130
And folks who are joining
remotely-- welcome, as well.

00:00:08.130 --> 00:00:11.250
Today we have a very, very
special speaker-- someone

00:00:11.250 --> 00:00:14.750
whose work I deeply admire
and have been fond of.

00:00:14.750 --> 00:00:18.360
I was thinking about what is
the best way to introduce him?

00:00:18.360 --> 00:00:21.430
Should I say he is a Managing
Director at Credit Suisse?

00:00:21.430 --> 00:00:25.760
Should I say he's an Adjunct
Professor at Columbia?

00:00:25.760 --> 00:00:30.230
Usually not all practitioners
